item.description:
We took a few weeks off but tennis related fun never really goes away so let's try to get the group together again.

Compared to this week's swelter, Saturday looks to be a little cooler plus let's start a bit earlier at 9:30. You can show up whenever you like but know that I'll be there early. Feel comfortable to come regardless of your abilities.

Bring water, get some exersize and hopefully connect with some happenin' people.

Call 860-561-8941 with questions or comments. I hope to see you there.

group.name: The West Hartford Over 40 Fun Bunch!
